== Events == * {{ill|Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13 ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|685|ja|685th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} establishes the tradition of rebuilding its main sanctuary every 20 years, known as {{ill|Shikinen Sengu|ja|式年遷宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Sejong the Great|ja|世宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 28 (Julian {{ill|1446|ja|1446年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – King {{ill|Sejong the Great|ja|世宗 (朝鮮王)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Joseon|ja|李氏朝鮮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} distributes the explanatory book on {{ill|Hangul|ja|ハングル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 『{{ill|Hunminjeongeum|ja|訓民正音|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 』 (Hangul Day). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The fiercest battle of the {{ill|Battle of Kawanakajima|ja|川中島の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} occurs (known as the Battle of Hachimanbara).
== Births == * {{ill|Kenkū|ja|建久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 (Julian {{ill|1197|ja|1197th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Juntoku|ja|順徳天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 84th Emperor of Japan (+ {{ill|1242|ja|1242nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya Yukihito|ja|有栖川宮職仁親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 5th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} house (+ {{ill|1769|ja|1769th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1725|ja|1725th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Shigetaka|ja|毛利重就|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 8th lord of {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and 8th lord of {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1789|ja|1789th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kimura Hisashi|ja|木村栄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|List of Japanese astronomers|ja|日本の天文学者の一覧|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Enchō|ja|延長 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Julian {{ill|927|ja|927th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shinjaku Hōshinnō|ja|真寂法親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Prince-monk|ja|法親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|886|ja|886年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平 (日本)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7 / {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Julian {{ill|1352|ja|1352nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Satake Sadayoshi|ja|佐竹貞義|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1287|ja|1287th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kakitsu|ja|Kakitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Julian {{ill|1441|ja|1441st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 25|ja|9月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Akamatsu Mitsusuke|ja|赤松満祐|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Muromachi period|ja|室町時代|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Shugo Daimyō|ja|守護大名|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1381|ja|1381st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ?). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Nobushige|ja|武田信繁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1525|ja|1525th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1645|ja|1645th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Uesugi Sadakatsu|ja|上杉定勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 2nd lord of {{ill|Yonezawa Domain|ja|米沢藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1604|ja|1604th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Gregorian {{ill|1704|ja|1704th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mukai Kyorai|ja|向井去来|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , one of the {{ill|Shōmon Jitte|ja|Shōmon Jūtetsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1714|ja|1714th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takemoto Gidayū|ja|竹本義太夫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , founder of {{ill|Gidayū-bushi|ja|義太夫節|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9 (Gregorian {{ill|1797|ja|1797th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Rokugo Masaharu|ja|六郷政林|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 6th lord of {{ill|Honjō Domain|ja|本荘藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1737|ja|1737th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
