esugi Sadakatsu|ja|上杉定勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 2nd lord of {{ill|Yonezawa Domain|ja|米沢藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1604|ja|1604th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Gregorian {{ill|1704|ja|1704th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mukai Kyorai|ja|向井去来|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , one of the {{ill|Shōmon Jitte|ja|Shōmon Jūtetsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1714|ja|1714th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takemoto Gidayū|ja|竹本義太夫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , founder of {{ill|Gidayū-bushi|ja|義太夫節|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9 (Gregorian {{ill|1797|ja|1797th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Rokugo Masaharu|ja|六郷政林|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 6th lord of {{ill|Honjō Domain|ja|本荘藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1737|ja|1737th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
