{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 10''' is the 10th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|685|ja|685th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} establishes the tradition of rebuilding its main sanctuary every 20 years, known as {{ill|Shikinen Sengu|ja|式年遷宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Sejong the Great|ja|世宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 28 (Julian {{ill|1446|ja|1446年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – King {{ill|Sejong the Great|ja|世宗 (朝鮮王)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Joseon|ja|李氏朝鮮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} distributes the explanatory book on {{ill|Hangul|ja|ハングル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 『{{ill|Hunminjeongeum|ja|訓民正音|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 』 (Hangul Day). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The fiercest battle of the {{ill|Battle of Kawanakajima|ja|川中島の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} occurs (known as the Battle of Hachimanbara).
== Births == * {{ill|Kenkū|ja|建久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 (Julian {{ill|1197|ja|1197th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Juntoku|ja|順徳天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 84th Emperor of Japan (+ {{ill|1242|ja|1242nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya Yukihito|ja|有栖川宮職仁親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 5th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} house (+ {{ill|1769|ja|1769th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1725|ja|1725th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Shigetaka|ja|毛利重就|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 8th lord of {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and 8th lord of {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1789|ja|1789th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kimura Hisashi|ja|木村栄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|List of Japanese astronomers|ja|日本の天文学者の一覧|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
