== Births == * {{ill|Kenkū|ja|建久|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 8 (Julian {{ill|1197|ja|1197th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Juntoku|ja|順徳天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 84th Emperor of Japan (+ {{ill|1242|ja|1242nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya Yukihito|ja|有栖川宮職仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 5th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} house (+ {{ill|1769|ja|1769th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1725|ja|1725th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Shigetaka|ja|毛利重就|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 8th lord of {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and 8th lord of {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1789|ja|1789th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kimura Hisashi|ja|木村栄|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|List of Japanese astronomers|ja|日本の天文学者の一覧|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Enchō|ja|延長 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 (Julian {{ill|927|ja|927th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shinjaku Hōshinnō|ja|真寂法親王|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Prince-monk|ja|法親王|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|886|ja|886年|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 7 / {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 (Julian {{ill|1352|ja|1352nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Satake Sadayoshi|ja|佐竹貞義|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1287|ja|1287th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kakitsu|ja|Kakitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 (Julian {{ill|1441|ja|1441st year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|September 25|ja|9月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Akamatsu Mitsusuke|ja|赤松満祐|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Muromachi period|ja|室町時代|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|Shugo Daimyō|ja|守護大名|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1381|ja|1381st year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ?). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Nobushige|ja|武田信繁|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1525|ja|1525th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1645|ja|1645th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Uesugi Sadakatsu|ja|上杉定勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 2nd lord of {{ill|Yonezawa Domain|ja|米沢藩|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1604|ja|1604th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 (Gregorian {{ill|1704|ja|1704th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mukai Kyorai|ja|向井去来|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , one of the {{ill|Shōmon Jitte|ja|Shōmon Jūtetsu|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1714|ja|1714th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takemoto Gidayū|ja|竹本義太夫|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , founder of {{ill|Gidayū-bushi|ja|義太夫節|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 9 (Gregorian {{ill|1797|ja|1797th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Rokugo Masaharu|ja|六郷政林|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 6th lord of {{ill|Honjō Domain|ja|本荘藩|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1737|ja|1737th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
