== Births == * {{ill|Kenkū|ja|建久|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 8 (Julian {{ill|1197|ja|1197th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Juntoku|ja|順徳天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 84th Emperor of Japan (+ {{ill|1242|ja|1242nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya Yukihito|ja|有栖川宮職仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 5th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} house (+ {{ill|1769|ja|1769th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1725|ja|1725th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Shigetaka|ja|毛利重就|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 8th lord of {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and 8th lord of {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1789|ja|1789th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kimura Hisashi|ja|木村栄|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|List of Japanese astronomers|ja|日本の天文学者の一覧|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
