== Births == * {{ill|Kenkū|ja|建久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8 (Julian {{ill|1197|ja|1197th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Juntoku|ja|順徳天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 84th Emperor of Japan (+ {{ill|1242|ja|1242nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya Yukihito|ja|有栖川宮職仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 5th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} house (+ {{ill|1769|ja|1769th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1725|ja|1725th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Shigetaka|ja|毛利重就|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 8th lord of {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and 8th lord of {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1789|ja|1789th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kimura Hisashi|ja|木村栄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|List of Japanese astronomers|ja|日本の天文学者の一覧|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Enchō|ja|延長 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1 (Julian {{ill|927|ja|927th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shinjaku Hōshinnō|ja|真寂法親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Prince-monk|ja|法親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (* {{ill|886|ja|886年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 7 / {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1 (Julian {{ill|1352|ja|1352nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Satake Sadayoshi|ja|佐竹貞義|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (* {{ill|1287|ja|1287th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kakitsu|ja|Kakitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1 (Julian {{ill|1441|ja|1441st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|September 25|ja|9月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Akamatsu Mitsusuke|ja|赤松満祐|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Muromachi period|ja|室町時代|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Shugo Daimyō|ja|守護大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (* {{ill|1381|ja|1381st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ?). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Nobushige|ja|武田信繁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (* {{ill|1525|ja|1525th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1645|ja|1645th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Uesugi Sadakatsu|ja|上杉定勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 2nd lord of {{ill|Yonezawa Domain|ja|米沢藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (* {{ill|1604|ja|1604th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1 (Gregorian {{ill|1704|ja|1704th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Mukai Kyorai|ja|向井去来|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Haiku poet|ja|Hai