'''September 10''' is the 10th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . 


== Events ==
* {{ill|Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  13 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|685|ja|685th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  establishes the tradition of rebuilding its main sanctuary every 20 years, known as {{ill|Shikinen Sengu|ja|式年遷宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Sejong the Great|ja|世宗|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  28 (Julian {{ill|1446|ja|1446年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – King {{ill|Sejong the Great|ja|世宗 (朝鮮王)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  of {{ill|Joseon|ja|李氏朝鮮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  distributes the explanatory book on {{ill|Hangul|ja|ハングル|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 『{{ill|Hunminjeongeum|ja|訓民正音|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 』 (Hangul Day).
* {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – The fiercest battle of the {{ill|Battle of Kawanakajima|ja|川中島の戦い|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  occurs (known as the Battle of Hachimanbara).

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kenkū|ja|建久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  8 (Julian {{ill|1197|ja|1197th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Juntoku|ja|順徳天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 84th Emperor of Japan (+ {{ill|1242|ja|1242nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya Yukihito|ja|有栖川宮職仁親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 5th head of the {{ill|Arisugawa-no-miya|ja|有栖川宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  house (+ {{ill|1769|ja|1769th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  10 (Gregorian {{ill|1725|ja|1725th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Shigetaka|ja|毛利重就|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 8th lord of {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  and 8th lord of {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (+ {{ill|1789|ja|1789th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1870|ja|1870th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kimura Hisashi|ja|木村栄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|List of Japanese astronomers|ja|日本の天文学者の一覧|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (+ {{ill|1943|ja|1943rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).

