* {{ill|Enchō|ja|延長 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  1 (Julian {{ill|927|ja|927th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shinjaku Hōshinnō|ja|真寂法親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Prince-monk|ja|法親王|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (* {{ill|886|ja|886年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
