* {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  4 (Julian {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Nobushige|ja|武田信繁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (* {{ill|1525|ja|1525th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  2 (Gregorian {{ill|1645|ja|1645th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Uesugi Sadakatsu|ja|上杉定勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 2nd lord of {{ill|Yonezawa Domain|ja|米沢藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (* {{ill|1604|ja|1604th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  1 (Gregorian {{ill|1704|ja|1704th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Mukai Kyorai|ja|向井去来|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , one of the {{ill|Shōmon Jitte|ja|Shōmon Jūtetsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Shōtoku|ja|正徳 (日本)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  4 (Gregorian {{ill|1714|ja|1714th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Takemoto Gidayū|ja|竹本義太夫|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , founder of {{ill|Gidayū-bushi|ja|義太夫節|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (* {{ill|1651|ja|1651st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
